i3wm Keybindings Cheat Sheet
=============================

 = Super/Windows key

## Window Management
+Return         Start ghostty terminal
+q              Kill focused window
+f              Toggle fullscreen

## Focus
+j/k/b/o        Focus left/down/up/right
+Left/Down/Up/Right  Focus with arrow keys
+a              Focus parent container
+space          Toggle focus tiling/floating

## Move Windows
+Shift+j/k/b/o  Move window left/down/up/right
+Shift+Arrows   Move window with arrow keys

## Layout
+h              Split horizontal
+v              Split vertical
+s              Stacking layout
+g              Tabbed layout
+e              Toggle split
+Shift+space    Toggle floating
+r              Resize mode (use arrows, Esc to exit)

## Workspaces
+1-0            Switch to workspace 1-10
+Shift+1-0      Move window to workspace 1-10
+Tab            Next workspace
+Shift+Tab      Previous workspace
+Shift+n        Open new empty workspace

## Applications
+w              Open Brave browser
+n              Open Thunar file manager
+d              Rofi app launcher
+t              Rofi window switcher
+p              Switch audio output
+Shift+p        Power profiles menu
Print           Screenshot (select region)

## System
+l              Lock screen (blur)
+Shift+c        Reload i3 config
+Shift+r        Restart i3
+Shift+e        Power/exit menu
F1              Keybindings help (rofi)

## Media Keys
XF86Audio*      Volume up/down/mute
XF86MonBrightness*  Brightness up/down
XF86AudioPlay/Next/Prev  Media controls
